Partners





At Longview we consider our partners an extension of our global team and an integral component of our development and growth. We align with leading consulting, implementation, and technology companies that have specific domain expertise. Combining Longview with our partners’ experience enables us to help organizations achieve better insights from their data.

Contact for North America


Contact for EMEA, APAC, LATAM


Access the arc|community


Access the Tidemark Community

Join the Partners Network
 
Technology

Many of the world's most respected companies use our technology platform to support the diverse needs of their complex financing organizations. Together with our partners, we offer a comprehensive solution for our CPM and tax customers. Longview has long-standing partnerships with leading technology providers and consulting companies. This gives our customers access to the tools they need to achieve the best business performance. All our partners are established in the industry and provide our customers with additional technology and consulting support by optimizing our software solution for CPM and taxation and providing best practices for the business processes of our customers.

Technology Partner

 
Certificates

Systems Integrators
Please contact Longview at partners@longview.com if your firm has strong domain expertise and would be interested in assisting us in large enterprise integrations  
 
OEM Partners
Many organizations benefit from deploying our industry-leading Unified Optimization Platform “powered by Longview.”   Please contact partners@longview.com for more information. 
 
Tax Service Providers

Our Tax Service Providers provide best-in-class, value-added services surrounding Longview Tax, including:
Review of tax data collection, provision and accounting processes
Best practice process redesign, improvement and automation
Customer augmentation of Longview Tax
Project Management
Implementation and testing support
Accounting services
Advice on internal controls, including Sarbanes-Oxley
Advice on IFRS, US GAAP and Canadian tax provisioning
Longview offers solid end-to-end customer service, including consultation and 24/7 technical support. As part of our commitment to customer service, we also work with several trusted Tax Service Providers to help them deliver best-in-class, value added consultation services. Longview Tax TSP Training & Certification Program ensures they are qualified as a Longview Tax solution expert.
